type MarketplaceDailySnapshot @entity @dailySnapshot {
       " { Contract address }-{# of days since Unix epoch time} " 
       id: ID!

       " The marketplace that this snapshot belongs to. " 
       marketplace: Marketplace!

       " Block number where the snapshot is taken. " 
       blockNumber: BigInt!

       " Block timestamp when the snapshot is taken. " 
       timestamp: BigInt!

       " Number of collections listed on the marketplace. " 
       collectionCount: Int!

       " Cumulative trade volume (in ETH) " 
       cumulativeTradeVolumeETH: BigDecimal!

       " Revenue that goes to the marketplace protocol, aka protocol fee. " 
       marketplaceRevenueETH: BigDecimal!

       " Revenue that goes to creator, aka royalty fee. " 
       creatorRevenueETH: BigDecimal!

       " Sum of marketplaceRevenueETH and creatorRevenueETH. " 
       totalRevenueETH: BigDecimal!

       " Trade count of the all collections on the marketplace. " 
       tradeCount: Int!

       " Cumulative unique traders " 
       cumulativeUniqueTraders: Int!

       " Daily active traders " 
       dailyActiveTraders: Int!

       " Number of traded collections of the day " 
       dailyTradedCollectionCount: Int!

       " Number of traded items of the day " 
       dailyTradedItemCount: Int!

type MarketplaceDailySnapshot @entity @dailySnapshot {
       " The structure of the ID is as follows: { Contract address }-{# of days since Unix epoch time} " 
       id: ID!

       " A reference to the marketplace entity that this snapshot belongs to. " 
       marketplace: Marketplace!

       " The block number, from the corresponding network, of the block that the transaction that the snapshot was taken in. " 
       blockNumber: BigInt!

       " The timestamp associated with the block that the snapshot transaction was taken in. " 
       timestamp: BigInt!

       " Number of NFT collections listed on the OpenSea marketplace at the time of the snapshot. " 
       collectionCount: Int!

       " Cumulative trading volume (in Ether, formatted as a decimal) at the time of the snapshop for the given Marketplace. " 
       cumulativeTradeVolumeETH: BigDecimal!

       " Revenue, aka protocol fee, that goes to the marketplace protocol that is collected during protocol operations. " 
       marketplaceRevenueETH: BigDecimal!

       " Revenue that goes to creator, aka royalty fee, in Ether (formatted as a decimal). " 
       creatorRevenueETH: BigDecimal!

       " The toal Ether revenue collected at the time of the snapshot, which is the sum of the Marketplace revenue and the Creator revenue. " 
       totalRevenueETH: BigDecimal!

       " Trade count of the all collections on the marketplace protocol at the time of the snapshot. " 
       tradeCount: Int!

       " The cumulative number of unique traders on the protocol at the time of the snapshot, as a count of unique addresses that have traded on the protocol. " 
       cumulativeUniqueTraders: Int!

       " The daily active trader count for the protocol based upon a count of user addresses. " 
       dailyActiveTraders: Int!

       " The number of traded NFT collections for a given day on the protocol at the time of the snapshot. " 
       dailyTradedCollectionCount: Int!

       " The number of traded items, NFTs, on a given day at the time of the snapshot. " 
       dailyTradedItemCount: Int!
